# LCD graphic animation example # {#HERO_BOARD_EXAMPLE_ANIMATION}

This example displays 8 graphic images in succesion on the Graphic LCD to form 
an animation:

![](boards/arm/stm32/px_hero/examples/animation/res/animation.gif)

Image source: [NUTS & VOLTS: Building your own Bitmaps and Animation for the 128x64 Graphics Kit](http://www.nutsvolts.com/blog/post/building_your_own_bitmaps_and_animation_for_the_128x64_graphics_kit)
  
File(s):
- boards/arm/stm32/px_hero/examples/animation/src/main.c

The following modules are used:
- @ref BOARDS_STM32_PX_HERO
- @ref STM32_SPI
- @ref PX_LCD_ST7567_JHD12864
- @ref PX_GFX
